{"categories":["product-launch","media-entertainment","gaming"],"collections":"","description":"Experience the thrill and excitement of the ultimate racing adventure with our latest car videogame. Immerse yourself in a world of speed and dust, where you can feel the earth beneath your wheels and the wind in your hair. This gaming experience is crafted in hues of beige, blue, and brown, creating an atmosphere that's as dark and mysterious as it is exhilarating. Don't just watch video, be a part of the action. Get ready to race and make every second count. This product launch is not just about entertainment, but about stepping into a world where you can truly feel the thrill of the chase. So, gear up, get it, and let the race begin!","short_description":"Immerse in our latest car videogame's world of speed, dust, and thrill. Crafted in rich hues of beige, blue, and brown, this gaming experience is more than just entertainment. Don't just watch video, be part of the action. Gear up, race, and feel the adrenaline rush. Get it now and let the adventure begin!","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/matteo-della-chiesa.jpg","description":"I've started to use Photoshop when I was 13. From 2009 to 2014, I've been a part of 5 Art Groups, doing Illustrations and Photo-manipulations, collaborating with over 150 Artists from all the Planet. In 2014, during my final school's exams, I've got my first Freelance Job at a Milan based Agency. Thanks to that first project, I started my Career as a Freelance Independent UI & Web Designer. Today, I help brands improve their online and digital presence, building usable, unique & beautiful products, mostly collaborating with Italian & US Agencies and Startups.","short_description":"","display_name":"Matteo Della Chiesa","id":"matteo-della-chiesa"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head><title></titl